潔的面容、淨色T恤配恤衫⋯<br />\n是有書卷氣息的男生。<br />\n阿靜身邊放著袋子，我只好坐這男生身旁。<br />\n我感覺到他看著我。<br />\n5－4－3－2－1。<br />\n五秒定律。<br />\n⋯⋯<br />\n⋯⋯<br />\n⋯⋯<br />\n吓？！他竟然沒有和我說話！為甚麼？！<br />\n<br />\nA. 主動交談<br />\nB. 默默觀察"},{"pid":"5261bf6898a6218f7af111697a2b1d88d67587c9","tid":953133,"uid":141555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T06:06:59.000Z","msg":"a"},{"pid":"b02c337fbc881f705cd089a1d41e2866ea161149","tid":953133,"uid":37537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T06:13:57.000Z","msg":"B<br />\n死港女一定係拎埋一面西住面咁射喱目及"},{"pid":"08178677690562fdd9c808ab38869679c3d0de41","tid":953133,"uid":34411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T06:55:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dbccaa82dfc3c94864af1dfe014e3271e321281a","tid":953133,"uid":135475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T06:57:19.000Z","msg":"B"},{"pid":"918c0a1ac2033b8292650f56323e1b88f3e5f52a","tid":953133,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T07:51:55.000Z","msg":"B"},{"pid":"fc754bbf03a460f0508c831e994a03b3e90571a3","tid":953133,"uid":164932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T08:58:50.000Z","msg":"A"},{"pid":"0b76a7ae02a8142c28ecd18c18475c30f09459fd","tid":953133,"uid":228058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T10:48:37.000Z","msg":"竟然有男生看著我五秒後沒有說話，難道他是驚呆了？<br />\n我決定默默觀察這人，他的反應令我很在意。<br />\n<br />\n「好，呢課嘅group project嘅題目係喺學校入面做一啲活動，令其他同學感受到溫暖。」課堂已經開始，Lecturer在簡介科目要求。<br />\n「噏乜鳩⋯⋯」旁邊的人細細碎語。<br />\n這題目真是莫名其妙。早聽說Asso的科目參差，沒想到要這麼有創意⋯<br />\n「咁不如就我哋一組啦！」阿靜真是個主動的女生，看來她是想接近那毒撚。<br />\n「好！Terry你都一齊啦。」毒撚望著那男生。<br />\n原來他叫Terry。<br />\n「霖，你會同我一齊㗎嘛？」阿靜對我眨眨眼。<br />\n「OK。」我也想看看這個Terry有何特別，只是一科Group Project，和誰組也沒大分別。<br />\n<br />\n「咁我開個group先！」看來毒撚真的挺迫不急待，但對不起，只需一眼就能確定我跟你連0.0001%的可能也沒有，能跟我做groupmate已是你的福氣！我還是好好幫阿靜，撮合你們。<br />\n<br />\n「叫咩Group名好？」毒撚問。<br />\n<br />\nA. 型男俊女團<br />\nB. 開放答案（揀最多正評）"},{"pid":"b14bbf583aba054295e3cfe1d4d4cf4266b9cbec","tid":953133,"uid":36441,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:52:50.000Z","msg":"哪來的自信組"},{"pid":"dd6edd8fa1d08c87852137e2a77c23b2d9702f0f","tid":953133,"uid":227801,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T15:06:29.000Z","msg":"升U上車團"},{"pid":"587af866addb3dcfb4c60d30bbbd0b9ff61b433a","tid":953133,"uid":37746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T15:43:40.000Z","msg":"狗與臭蟹sss"},{"pid":"f9e9a6a57d56c2f04f80dd2438559f79c00df491","tid":953133,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T15:45:19.000Z","msg":"波都冇學人出故<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74625287b0aebd6b992430d0feb3df74f36cfc77","tid":953133,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T15:53:22.000Z","msg":"樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43e1c13eda7e7aeeac23e1057fac9074dc3bf5e4","tid":953133,"uid":17453,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T15:53:44.000Z","msg":"仲有啲橙皮team"}]}